# Architecture: File Discovery

**Version:** 1.0
**Status:** Draft
**Spec:** [Feature Spec](../1-requirements/file_discovery/file_discovery.spec)

## Components

| Component | Traces To | Description |
|-----------|-----------|-------------|
| FR-200 handler | SYS-02 -> `core/scanner.rs` | The scanner shall recursively discover all files under the provided project root directory. |
| FR-201 handler | SYS-02 -> `core/scanner.rs` | The scanner shall skip: hidden directories (names starting with `.`), `target/`, `node_modules/`. |
| FR-202 handler | SYS-02 -> `core/scanner.rs` | All discovered file paths shall be relative to the project root. |

